If you really want to make money…
.
You could do what you love and monetize your passion…
.
You could innovate a hobby and show others how to do it…
.
You could even become an expert and create a @lightspeed_vt course on it…
.
OR you could solve a really big problem and find out what REAL money is.
.
Whatever your product, make sure it solves a problem, that’s the #1 thing that will make you 💰💰💰.
